OL,3,CIrwin's bakery: Former sales manager
OL,4,Csettles age discrimination case for
OL,5,C#75,000
OL,7,FA 60-year-old man has settled an age
OL,8,Fdiscrimination case against his former
OL,9,Femployer, Irwin's bakery, for #75,000.
OL,11,FSeamus Gillespie, who was a sales
OL,12,Fmanager, alleged he was told the
OL,13,Fcompany was looking for younger
OL,14,Fprofessional people as part of a
OL,15,Frecruitment drive.
OL,17,FThe case was supported by the Equality
OL,18,FCommission for Northern Ireland and
OL,19,Fwas settled without admission of
OL,20,Fliability by the company.
